      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>Your nanites utilize electrical pulses to cause exhausting muscle spasms and electrical interference. Weapons you form with your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.LLNp1urkLncOxgsb]{gear array} gain the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.O5GDQUKPCJ9Zbnfj.JournalEntryPage.zOJ86MDq6kNzAAbB#fatigue]{fatigue} critical hit effect (Starfinder Armory31). Once per day, after you damage a creature with a weapon formed from your gear array, you can use a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.vh6n0Ad3lamOJXpV]{nanite surge} as a reaction to impose the effects of @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.4prroV3z26u1cy5y]{slow}on the target (Fortitude negates) for a number of rounds equal to half your Constitution bonus. Creatures immune to electricity are immune to exhausting nanites.</p>"
